Package remixlab.bias.branch

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Action<E extends Enum<E>>
    Generic interface defining user action (sub)groups.
    GenericGrabber<E extends Enum<E>>
    The root of Grabber objects that may implement user-defined actions specified by an enum type.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Branch<E extends Enum<E>>
    A Branch handles a list of GenericGrabber objects (Branch.grabbers(), implementing the same reference action set used to parameterize it.
    GenericAgent
    A Agent extended with branches, see GenericMotionAgent.appendBranch(String), GenericKeyboardAgent.appendBranch(String).
    GenericEventGrabberTuple<E extends Enum<E>>
    A [BogusEvent,GenericGrabber, Action] tuple.
    GenericGrabberObject<E extends Enum<E>>
    Default implementation of the GenericGrabber interface which eases implementation.
    GenericKeyboardAgent
    An Agent to which KeyboardBranches may be appended (see GenericKeyboardAgent.appendBranch(String)).
    GenericMotionAgent
    An Agent that handles MotionBranches (see GenericMotionAgent.appendBranch(String)).
    KeyboardBranch<E extends Enum<E>,A extends Action<E>>
    A Branch with a single KeyboardBranch.keyboardProfile(), defining some KeyboardShortcut / (keyboard) action mappings.
    MotionBranch<E extends Enum<E>,A extends Action<E>,C extends Action<E>>
    A Branch with a MotionBranch.motionProfile(), defining some MotionShortcut / (motion) action mappings; and a MotionBranch.clickProfile(), defining some ClickShortcut / (click) action mappings.
    Profile<E extends Enum<E>,K extends Shortcut,A extends Action<E>>
    A mapping defining Shortcut to Action bindings, implemented as a parameterized hash-map wrap.
